Nighal 10: It is the power, the limitless power. That is the source. The
	spirits now wander the upper halls of cathedral, lashing out at any
	who crosses them. I have sent the others to the first floor and told
	them to stay there. The power has no direction save that I give it.
	When I invoked it when I was mad, I gave it madness. How long before
	the strain of the Life and the madness pulls me apart?

